name: Black Tie Service (B4R0N $4M3DI'$ Variant)
description:
The original variant was a color inversion stroke of luck, the second one the happy meeting of a filter and a program to reduce the image to the level of 16 bit graphics..

This one has an ASCII embellishment thanks to a comment on Twitter by @maxcapacity about the software he's been using for his art, and admiration for the ASCII art of @dr3amer_r who has been making some amazing animation with ASCII characters..
